and as a data scientist I came somewhere that had, you know, larger than memory data in

00:00:45.959 --> 00:00:50.959
databases that I kind of had to learn how to use and now I work at Posit building tools

00:00:50.959 --> 00:00:56.680
for people and all the kind of experiences I had in the past about what do I do when

00:00:56.680 --> 00:01:04.120
I cannot like deal with my data in memory on my laptop, I feel like all those experiences

00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:10.120
have led me to think, you know what, I learned about these in a very, a model that was like

00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:15.760
an apprenticeship style model without like thinking it was, often thinking it was specific

