So, when I think about like my own path with this and I think about it now, I'm like, oh,

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:32.720
it would be really helpful for all of us to have some shared understanding of what the

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:36.000
options are and what some of these trade-offs are.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:44.400
So, we almost all start out, maybe if you are in a class in a, you know, maybe a data

